noted.', 'Synergism, Excretion', 'If possible, drugs that are potentially nephrotoxic including NSAIDs should be avoided during the 5 days of clofarabine administration.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/8036/', '', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole, Homatropine, Atropine, Scopolamine, Methscopolamine, Ephedrine, Tropicamide, More', 'Fluorouracil, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine', 1767369485);
